Quickstrike:




Quickstrike opened his optics, hearing Black Aracnia's voice. He 
heard her question about the offspring. He lifted his head up and 
looked over to where she was addressing. The offspring was sitting by 
the end of the bunk, leaning up against it, with her back turned. She 
obviously heard her. She turned her head to them.

"Yeah," he said lightly.
